quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  53,33,“Kodi wamuona yemwe wadzipatula (pakusiya kutsatira choonadi)
  53,34,“Ndipo wapereka (chuma) chochepa nasiyanso kuperekako
  53,35,"“Kodi akudziwa zamseri, kotero kuti akuziwona (zomwe wadza nazo (Mtumiki {s.a.w) kuti sizoona"
  53,36,“Kapena sadauzidwe zomwe zidali m’mabuku a Mûsa
  53,37,“Ndi Ibrahim amene adakwaniritsa (lonjezo la Allah)
  53,38,“Kuti mzimu wamachimo sungasenze machimo a mzimu wina
  53,39,“Ndi kutinso munthu sakalipidwa koma zimene adachita
  53,40,“Ndipo ndithu ntchito zake zidzaonekera
  53,41,“Kenako (munthu) adzalipidwa malipiro okwanira (pa ntchito zake zimene amachita)
  53,42,“Ndipo ndithu kwa Mbuye wako yekha ndiwo malekezero (a chilichonse)
  53,43,“Ndithu Iye ndiAmene amapereka chisangalalo ndi zoliritsa
  53,44,“Ndipo Iye yekha ndi Amene amapereka imfa ndi moyo
  53,45,"“Ndipo Iye ndiAmene adalenga mitundu iwiri: chachimuna ndi chachikazi, (anthu ndi zamoyo zina)"
  53,46,“Kuchokera m’mbewu ya moyo pamene imafwamphukira (m’chiberekero)
  53,47,“Ndipo ndithu ndi udindo Wake kuukitsa kwina (pambuyo pa imfa)
  53,48,“Ndipo Iye ndiAmene amapatsa chokwanira ndipo ndi amene amapatsa chosunga
  53,49,“Ndipo ndithu Iye ndi Mbuye wa nyenyezi yotchedwa Shiira
  53,50,“Ndipo Iye ndi amene adaononga Âdi oyamba; (anthu a Mneneri Hûd)
  53,51,“Ndi Samudu; (anthu a Mneneri Swaleh;) choncho sadasiye (ndi mmodzi yemwe wa iwo)
  53,52,"“Ndipo (adawaononganso) anthu a Nuh, kale (asadaononge Âdi ndi Samudu). Ndithu iwo adali osalungama ndi olumpha malire kwambiri (kuposa Âdi ndi Samudu)"
  53,53,"“Ndi midzi yotembenuzidwa kumwamba kukhala pansi, pansi kukhala kumwamba, (ya anthu a Luti) adaigwetsa"
  53,54,“Tero chidaivindikira (midziyo) chomwe chidaivindikira (chilango)
  53,55,“Kodi ndimtendere uti (mumtendere) wa Mbuye wako umene ukuukaikira
  53,56,“Uyu (Mtumiki) ndimchenjezi mwa achenjezi oyamba (amene adachenjezedwa nawo anthu a mibadwo yakale)
  53,57,“Chayandikira choyandikira (Qiyâma)
  53,58,“Palibe amene angachionetse koma Allah Yekha
  53,59,“Kodi mukuidabwa nkhaniyi (ya Qur’an moikana)
  53,60,“Mungoseka (mwachipongwe) ndipo simukulira (pamene mukuimva monga momwe akuchitira okhulupirira)
  53,61,“Ndipo mukunyozera
  53,62,“Mlambireni ndi kumpembedza Allah (amene wavumbulutsa Qur’an kuti ikhale chiongoko cha anthu)